      • getUsableCommands

        public java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getUsableCommands(Actor forWhom)
        Gets a Set with all commands usable for the given Actor.

        The commands are represented as Strings. Each command is prefixed with /, aliases are seperated by |.

        Parameters:
        forWhom - the Actor for whom the returned commands should be usable
        Returns:
        all usable commands as strings
